Utilities for Using Ryacas

Ivan Jacob Agaloos Pesigan 2021-02-18

Description

A collection of utility functions for using Ryacas.

Installation

You can install the released version of yacR from GitHub with:

remotes::install_github("jeksterslab/yacR")

See GitHub Pages for package documentation.
